content:
Load data into OmniScript elements using Omnistudio Data Mappers, Integration Procedures, HTTP Actions, URL parameters, or Apex.

Load Salesforce data into an OmniScript using a Data Mapper Turbo Action or Data Mapper Extract Action.

Prefill repeatable blocks with data by passing it in an array format.

Seed data into an OmniScript to prefill fields or add hidden nodes to the JSON response.

Set a default value for an element using the Default Value property, which can be overwritten if prefilled from a Data Mapper or JSON response.
title: Loading Data into OmniScript Elements
